Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\shad0\bord2\frz1.5\fs34\t(\fs32)\move(364.797,35,364.797,54,24,7323)\c&&HC9D4D7&}Warning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:03.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Viewers Sitting in Front of the Television,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:05.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the guys that appear in this anime are delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, please do not imitate what you see in this anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\b1\i0\bord0\blur0.3\fad(450,0)\c&HDADADA&\fs33\pos(410.717,49)}Do not imitate{\i1\fs40}!{\i0\fs33} Or this will happen{\i1\fs40}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}僕が泣いているのは とても悔しいからです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}Boku ga naite iru no wa totemo kuyashii kara desu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)}The reason I am crying is\Nbecause I am very frustrated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}人の尊さやさしさ 踏みにじられそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Hito no toutosa yasashisa fuminijiraresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}I feel as though the nobility and\Nkindness of man is being trampled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}力を示す者達は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Chikara o shimesu mono tachi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}しなやかさを失って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Shinayakasa o ushinatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:34.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Those who show their strength lose their grace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}ウソまみれドロまみれ じれったい風景でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uso-mamire doro-mamire jirettai fuukei desho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Covered in dirt and lies, isn't it a vexing sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}より強くしたたかに タフな生き方をしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Yori tsuyoku shitataka ni tafu na ikikata o shimashou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's live more strongly, fiercely, and tougher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}まっすぐ歩きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Massugu arukimasho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's walk straight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}風は向かい風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kaze wa mukai kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The wind is against us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ どけ どけ 後ろめたい奴はどけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke doke doke ushirometai yatsu wa doke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, move, move, those with\Na guilty conscience, move aside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}有象無象の町に 灯りをともせ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uzoumuzou no machi ni akari o tomose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Light up the town of riffraff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ そこ どけ 真実のお通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke soko doke shinjitsu no otouri da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, make way, truth is coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}正義の時代がくるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Seigi no jidai ga kuru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The era of justice will come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}希望の歌もあるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kibou no uta mo aru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}There are songs of hope too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}僕の命この世に 捧げてしまっていいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}Boku no inochi kono yo ni sasagete-shimatte ii sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)}I would happily sacrifice my life for this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:33.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dearest Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:38.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I, Takako Kamiyama, was able to get enrolled\Nin Cromartie Girls High School.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.07,0:01:40.99,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,0)\fnAveria Sans\i1\shad0\bord1\pos(347.804,345)\fs32\c&H7A1616&\3c&HFEDFD9&\bord2}Sudama!! Cromartie Girls High School
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:40.99,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,0)\fnAveria Sans\i1\shad0\bord1\pos(347.804,345)\fs32\c&H7A1616&\bord3\1a&Hff\3c&H711512&}Sudama!! Cromartie Girls High School
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:43.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I do hope to get used to the school
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:46.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,as quickly as possible and lead a healthy academic life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:47.17,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(500,0)}Takako Kamiyama (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:47.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.55,0:01:49.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm surrounded by young ladies from good families
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:51.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,who are like princesses, and I'm at a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:53.17,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fnArnold 2.1\bord12\shad0\c&H111111&\3c&HF1F0F1&\fs14\pos(422.576,58)\clip(m 387.5 40 l 388.625 64 455.375 64 454.25 40)}Kamiyama
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:59.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've been called a princess\Nsince I was in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:00.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:04.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've never dated a gentleman before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:06.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:10.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen who are fond of me give up\N before they confess their love for me and leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:14.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,thinking "She's out of my league."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:16.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And the nickname I got was
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:18.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"Miss Masako of Default Victories".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:18.03,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(351.203,394)}Masako of Default Victories (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:22.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll come out and say it,\Nyou all are nothing compared to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:22.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:28.41,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(215.253,394)\fad(50,370)}Akiko Maeda (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:26.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'd take lessons from dawn to dusk every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:28.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Of course, I've never lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:30.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I can talk trash and lay down \Na bitch slap at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:33.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm what you'd call an honest\Nto goodness princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:35.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've even won five against one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:38.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't quite get what you're saying, but what was your nickname?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Nickname?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:42.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My nickname was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:44.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I never really had a nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:46.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then you're no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:48.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Like, too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:49.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This isn't worth discussing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:50.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:52.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's no point if you don't\Nhave a nickname like
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:55.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"Fireball Princess of Junior 2"\N or "Monster Princess of Junior 3"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:58.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's right. If you're like\N"Suzuki of Junior 4" or "Satoh,"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:01.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,it doesn't give off the sense of\N"Like, that's sooo cool!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:02.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:04.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please try again next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:07.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay. Please accept my\Nchallenge again next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:09.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's no next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB7D2DC&}Aah! There's a gentleman here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:16.30,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fs52\blur0.4\fnSniglet\shad0\bord0\c&H8B7AF4&\move(487.152,99,497.348,86,0,4944)\t(\fs56)}FANCY CLUB
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:13.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In Takako Kamiyama's class,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:16.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,they decided that they'd determine\Nwho's the strongest princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:21.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To start with, I've picked up a couple of people\Nbased on their history of being princesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:22.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's these three.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:27.27,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fs31\b0\pos(152.943,385)\fad(0,150)}Main character
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:27.27,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fs31\b0\pos(152.943,455)\fad(0,150)}Takashi Kamiyama
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:24.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,477)}Please wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:26.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,477)}Why have I been nominated?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You silly girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:31.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Step back now, or I'll, like, fudging kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:33.81,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Shinjirobee Hayashida (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:33.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who nominated Miss Kamiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:35.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That is to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:38.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I want to see the devil that's in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:40.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I haven't the slightest what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:44.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, how are we going to decide\Nwho the strongest princess is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:45.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's got to be through jump-the-elastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:48.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You got that right!\NIt's got to be jump-the-elastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Setting aside the question of how it happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:54.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,they determined that Takako Kamiyama\Nwas the strongest princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:55.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I haven't introduced myself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:56.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm Tatsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:58.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dearest Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:04.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm at Year 1 Class 3 right now to see\NCromartie's incredible princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:07.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So the lady people are talking about is here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:10.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Freddie...
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.69,0:04:16.90,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\c&H1CD3C4&\bord0.5\blur1\fs50\frz10\t(\fs56)\fnJasmineUPC\move(532.468,245,544.93,245,0,3237)}Welcome \Nto the Jungle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:16.90,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\blur1\fs50\frz10\t(\fs55)\fnJasmineUPC\c&H116259&\move(534.734,247,546.063,247,0,3237)}Welcome \Nto the Jungle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Monsters dwell in Cromartie...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:18.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, then, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:21.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:24.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:33.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Miss Kamiyama, I heard that there's this\Nother gorgeous princess in another class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:36.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You've said the same thing each time,\Nyou know that, Miss Hayashida?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:39.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Anyway, she's gorgeous!\NI've never seen a princess like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:43.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's trouble, Lady Mechazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:47.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What seems to be the problem?\NMay I ask what you're rattled about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Lady Mechazawa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:52.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What a sober voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:55.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You birdbrain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:05:00.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How many times have I told you that you\Nshould not do things that are bad for your health?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:07.24,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\bord1\pos(368.196,394)}Shinichihime Mechazawa (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:07.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Who'll care for your mother if you're not around?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:09.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It was my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:13.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Lady Mechazawa is worried\N about you more than anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let us go now, Miss Hayashida.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:21.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's return to our class now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:32.47,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\pos(367.063,393)}Toyoko Takenouchi (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My name is Toyoko Takenouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm 16 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:32.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}I currently command the Year 1 at Cromartie\NGirls High School as their princess boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:36.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm very susceptible to motion sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:39.56,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\frx14\fry14\frz356.748\shad0\bord0\fs16\pos(347.804,148)\fnAveria Sans\c&H906465&}Restroom
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I want to throw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:39.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:42.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My name is Bushiko Hokuto. I'm 16 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:45.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My father is the chairman of the Hokuto Group
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:48.36,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(400,0)\pos(382.924,392)}Bushiko Hokuto (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:48.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}and also chairs the board of directors\Nfor Cromartie Girls High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:50.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,People are pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:53.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll hammer my ideals into the\Nheads of these incompetent pigs
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:54.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and control them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:54.79,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\bord01\pos(271.899,392)}Hokuto's Lackey (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:56.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:06:03.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My father is the chair of this high school.\NHe can even expel you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:05.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, this lady's saying strange things...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:08.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is a municipal school, so there's no chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:09.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:11.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, you really did it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:15.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hokuto and her lackey,\N who transferred to the wrong school,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,remained at Cromartie Girls High School
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:23.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and set off to the West with their friends\Nto become a princess who has no equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:28.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And, time passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:30.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Everyone, another transfer student has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:33.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let's welcome her, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:47.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:49.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"Sudama!! Cromartie Girls High School",
Dialogue: 2,0:06:48.51,0:06:57.77,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,0)\fnAveria Sans\i1\shad0\bord1\pos(347.804,315)\fs32\bord2\3c&HF3CBCB&\c&H701214&}Rosy Cromartie Girls High School
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.51,0:06:57.77,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,0)\fnAveria Sans\i1\shad0\bord1\pos(347.804,315)\fs32\c&H7A1616&\bord3\3c&H711512&\1a&Hff}Rosy Cromartie Girls High School
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:57.77,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,0)\fnAveria Sans\i1\shad0\bord1\pos(347.804,315)\fs32\c&H7A1616&\bord7\blur4\3c&HEFEDEC&\1a&Hff}Rosy Cromartie Girls High School
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:57.77,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,0)\fnAveria Sans\shad0\bord1\fs32\bord1\blur1\3c&HEFEDEC&\c&H1F1819&\pos(356.867,397)}End
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:52.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,we'd like to end it at this point for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:57.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Coming up, please enjoy\N"Sakigake!! Cromartie High School"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is Cromartie Municipal High School,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:04.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,a delinquent school everyone fears as the worst,\Nthe most terrible worst school in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:06.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In that den of iniquity,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:09.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,there are Year 2 guys who are senior to\NYear 1 Kamiyama and his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:14.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And among those Year 2 guys,\N there existed men who stood at the top of Year 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:14.24,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\frx40\fnBell Gothic Std Black\fs32\c&H5DF8FE&\3c&H330F3A&\4c&HDA1B88&\bord2\shad2\pos(367.063,58)}Tales of the The Four Lords of Cromartie
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:14.28,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\frx30\fnBell Gothic Std Black\fs32\c&H5DF8FE&\3c&H330F3A&\4c&HDA1B88&\bord2\shad2\pos(367.063,58)}Tales of the The Four Lords of Cromartie
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:14.33,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\frx15\fnBell Gothic Std Black\fs32\c&H5DF8FE&\3c&H330F3A&\4c&HDA1B88&\bord2\shad2\pos(367.063,58)}Tales of the The Four Lords of Cromartie
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:14.37,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\frx5\fnBell Gothic Std Black\fs32\c&H5DF8FE&\3c&H330F3A&\4c&HDA1B88&\bord2\shad2\pos(367.063,58)}Tales of the The Four Lords of Cromartie
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:18.16,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,900)\fnBell Gothic Std Black\fs32\c&H5DF8FE&\3c&H330F3A&\4c&HDA1B88&\bord2\shad2\pos(367.063,58)}Tales of the The Four Lords of Cromartie
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:15.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:17.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The Four Lords of Cromartie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:20.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We're facing a big problem right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.88,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnGrimace\c&H33322C&\shad0\bord0\frz347.57\pos(57.778,288)\blur0.4}Tardy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We're the Four Lords, but there are five of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:25.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, that being the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:27.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I think we'll take on an additional member.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:29.05,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fnBell Gothic Std Black\fs24\c&H5DF8FE&\3c&H330F3A&\4c&HDA1B88&\bord2\shad2\pos(217.519,41)}Tales of the The Four Lords of Cromartie
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:29.05,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fnAveria Sans\fs24\bord0.1\blur0.4\shad0\pos(219.785,141)\c&HECECEC&}End
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:27.25,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnGrimace\c&H33322C&\shad0\bord0\blur0.4\fs22\frz337.422\pos(-11.329,328)}Tardy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:27.30,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnGrimace\c&H33322C&\shad0\bord0\blur0.4\fs22\frz337.422\pos(30.589,328)}Tardy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:27.34,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnGrimace\c&H33322C&\shad0\bord0\blur0.4\fs22\frz337.422\pos(47.582,328)}Tardy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:29.05,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnGrimace\c&H33322C&\shad0\bord0\blur0.4\fs22\frz337.422\pos(52.114,328)}Tardy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:29.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:31.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, Maeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:34.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Have you ever thought about the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:36.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:40.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be unwise not to\Nthink about the future after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But, we're still in the 10th grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:46.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In any case, how far ahead\N are you saying we should think about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:48.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Getting employed, for starters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:52.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna be told such a thing\Nby someone with that hairstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:55.20,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\an7\fnAveria Sans\c&H302D28&\bord3\blur1\fs32\pos(5.665,5)\3c&HADB7A7&}Year 2 Class 2\NYearbook\NSoko Elementary School
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:54.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Take a little look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Huh? A yearbook?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:58.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I found it yesterday in the back of a closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:00.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It has my childhood dream written in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:02.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Would you read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:04.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sure. Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:07.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"I'd like to be a frog when I grow up.\N-Shinjiro Hayashida."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I guess you were a strange kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:15.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I have no clue what that was all about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:18.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But one thing I can say for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:22.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,is that I've always thought that\NI didn't want to live an ordinary life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:27.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I still want to carry out that belief from\Nhere on, even after becoming a delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:30.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kamiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:33.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We were discussing the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wasn't, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:36.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:37.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Future...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:40.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm not thinking about the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:41.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It is all I can do to live through today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:43.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:47.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I was thinking that you'd always be planning\Nyour future since you're a down-to-earth person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:50.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I got rid of such thoughts\Nwhen I entered this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:54.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I feel that I somehow was able to put various\Nthings behind me after coming to this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:55.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To get right to the point,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:57.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've become able to think\N"I don't care" in a good way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Take a little look outside the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:00.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:07.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I want you to be calm and think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:11.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't you think you'd be several hundred times\Nmore interested in their future than your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:14.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Certainly, I wonder where they'll get employed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:17.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, their employment\N or things like that isn't the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:20.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Of course, I think everyone\Nhas their own concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:22.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But when you think about\Na gorilla coming to school,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:24.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,any concern should seem small!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:27.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It certainly does. It seems silly to\Nworry about things, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:32.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In short, everyone tends to\N think about things selfishly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:33.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,However, the world is a big place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:37.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In other words, our concerns are still small.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:41.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But, Kamiyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:42.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What is it, Maeda?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:48.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's natural to worry about the future\Nsince we're at a stupid school like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:50.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Nothing'll come out of it even if we do graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:51.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Of course I'd worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:54.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, you should take a look out the window again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:55.44,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\fnAveria Sans\shad0\bord0\c&H131415&\frz90\pos(11.329,155)\fs36}Heave ho
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:55.44,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fnAveria Sans\shad0\bord0\c&H131415&\frz270\pos(704.671,155)\fs36}Heave ho
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:56.45,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\fnAveria Sans\shad0\bord0\c&H131415&\frz90\pos(11.329,155)\fs36}Heave ho
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:56.45,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fnAveria Sans\shad0\bord0\c&H131415&\frz270\pos(704.671,155)\fs36}Heave ho
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.49,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7\fnAveria Sans\shad0\bord0\c&H131415&\frz90\pos(11.329,155)\fs36}Heave ho
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.49,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fnAveria Sans\shad0\bord0\c&H131415&\frz270\pos(704.671,155)\fs36}Heave ho
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:57.95,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\an7\fnAveria Sans\shad0\bord0\c&H131415&\frz90\pos(11.329,155)\fs36}Heave ho
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:57.95,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\an9\fnAveria Sans\shad0\bord0\c&H131415&\frz270\pos(704.671,155)\fs36}Heave ho
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:57.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Heave ho, heave ho, heave ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:01.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why are they tossing him in the air? Are they celebrating something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:02.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't know the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:07.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But one thing I can say is that even those kind of\Npeople don't worry even 1 mm about their future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:12.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,When we look at those guys acting like that,\Nour small concerns will be blown away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:17.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I learned a lesson.\NNo concerns hold up against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:18.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:19.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You still have more to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:23.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even if you say that's the case,\NI still worry about the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:26.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're a persistent worrier.\NAre you really a delinquent?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:30.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Delinquents don't have a future in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're becoming a cruel guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:36.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you don't get it after all that explaining, I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:38.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Take a look out the window again.\NThis'll make you feel better...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:40.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Fzzrk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:41.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Zap zap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:42.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Pop...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:44.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,OH, NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:41.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,we'll end Sakigake!! Cromartie High School\Nwith this episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:42.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching for four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:44.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We've aired only a half-year!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.97,0:11:49.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs26\blur0.5\fnArial Black\bord3\c&H000000&\3c&HFBFAFC&\pos(190.329,50)}Sakigake!!\NCromartie High School
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:49.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs26\blur0.6\fnArial Black\bord3.2\c&H000000&\3c&H3F3F3F&\pos(190.329,50)}Sakigake!!\NCromartie High School
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:49.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\q2\fnArial Black\shad0\fs36\bord2.2\blur0.5\pos(385.19,390)\c&HFCFCFE&}We'll do it as many times as necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:46.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}It's fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:49.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,456)\c&HB7D2DC&}Please input your name after the voice instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:49.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}Man, what a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Intro Warning,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\blur0.3\pos(213.928,323.39)}When you are watching television
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Intro Warning,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\blur0.3\pos(587.096,341.559)}please have the room\Nbrightly lit and be\Ncareful not to get too\Nclose to the screen.
